        "timestamp": "2019-01-16 18:44:08.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review+1\n\none question, Jorge, where will this code be used, dmaap client in drools controller for pub/sub? I am a bit confused as I see jira says this is for management of drools templates and op policies but it looks more like general REST client. Just wondering how they can be connected here.",
