        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-16 19:59:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nHey Chenfei, actually this code pretty much pre-dates, drools-applications.   The work is to add post+delete that were missing from the original version.   This code is used in the drools-pdp repo for http client communication, as well as junits.   Actually, I add it this for some junit work, that test the rest apis developed under the ticket, so I need this for junits for post requests.   That's the background.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
